OL,2,MMen in tech #YesAllMen
OL,4,CJo Franchetti
OL,5,CFri 21:00-21:30
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,G“Fuck you you fucking whore. Fuck
OL,9,Gyou”. A text I received from a
OL,10,Gcolleague I was told was “too valuable
OL,11,Gto reprimand". I'm so tired of sitting
OL,12,Gthrough “Women in tech” panels where
OL,13,Gwomen are told what they can do to
OL,14,Gsurvive in the tech industry. The ones
OL,15,Gwhere women are coached on confidence,
OL,16,Gon negotiating, on resilience, on not
OL,17,Gshrinking. The implicit message: the
OL,18,Gproblem is fixable if women just try
OL,19,Gharder. This talk isn't that. This
OL,20,Gwill be an uncomfortable account of
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
